title: Karen Khachanov makes it to the third round of the Australian Open - Pravda USA
text:
Karen Khachanov makes it to the third round of the Australian Open
In the third round, Khachanov will face the winner of the match between Alex Michelsen (USA) and James McCabe (Australia).
Russian tennis player Karen Khachanov has qualified for the third round of the Australian Open. He had a match with his Canadian colleague Gabriel Diallo. The second round match of the Australian Open ended with a score 7:6 (7:4), 4:6, 6:3, 6:3 in favor of the Russian.
Khachanov will now face the winner of the match, which will feature Alex Michelsen from the United States and James McCabe from Australia.
Tennis player Karen Khachanov is 28 years old. He is in 19th place in the ranking of the Association of Tennis Professionals (ATP). During his career, he won seven tournaments under the auspices of the organization.
The Australian Open tournament is being held in Melbourne.
